    "The study highlights that these students depend on ChatGPT to facilitate the generation of research ideas, allowing them to save time and to produce high-quality research.",
    "Furthermore, ChatGPT is instrumental in assisting postgraduate students in the development of various research sections.",
    "These findings align with a study conducted by Aithal and Aithal (2023), emphasising the increasing ease with which students can conduct research and produce quality work through the assistance provided by a variety of AI tools, including ChatGPT.",
